I'm **Emily McCraken**, an artist and chocolatier. For the last 17 years I've worked at [Lake Champlain Chocolates](http://www.lakechamplainchocolates.com/) where I create retail specialty products, teach chocolate-related classes, and create [chocolate sculptures](https://www.chocolatesculptress.com).

My work has been featured on the [Food Network](https://www.foodnetwork.com/videos/cuckoo-for-chocolate-0235421), the [Dr. Oz Show](http://www.chocolatesculptress.com/journal/2014/dr-oz-chocolate-sculptures), and by [Mastercard's Priceless campaign](http://www.chocolatesculptress.com/press).

I live in northern Vermont with my [husband](https://scottmccracken.net), 6-year old daughter, and two rescue terrier muts.

